headline: Oceania Cruises® Unveils Reprise of Its Original French Restaurant, Jacques, With Ribbon-Cutting Ceremony on New Ship, Oceania Allura™
summary: Oceania Cruises®, the world's leading culinary- and destination-focused luxury cruise line, celebrated the reprisal of its signature French restaurant, Jacques, on board its newest ship, Oceania Allura™, with a special ribbon-cutting ceremony hosted by its namesake, the line's first-ever executive culinary director, Chef Jacques Pépin.
